GUNMEN in Aba, Abia State, have kidnapped a yet-to-be identified bureau de change operator. The incident, our reporter learnt, occurred at Okpu-Umuobo in Osisioma Local Government. The victim, said to be a newly wedded man, was reportedly taking his expectant wife home after she had gone for a medical check-up when the incident occurred. A source told our reporter that the kidnappers had contacted the family. “They are demanding N5million ransom,” the source said.